flowRoot.flowPara: CentOS is an Enterprise GNU/Linux distribution based on the freely available sources from Red Hat Enterprise Linux. Each CentOS version is supported for 7 years (by means of security updates).
A new CentOS version is release every 2 years and each CentOS version is regularly updated (every 6 months) to support newer hardware.
This results in a secure, low-maintenance, reliable, predictable and reproducible environment.
